                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Tripartite D–2, September 13, not printed, consisted of a cover sheet and the
                    text of the abbreviated Austrian peace treaty. For the text of the abbreviated
                    treaty, see volume IV.</p>
                <p>For the text of Tripartite D–3, September 14, see <gloss target="#t_WFM1"
                        >WFM</gloss> T–5<hi rend="italic">a</hi>, page 1197, and footnotes
                    thereto.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
